snippet.title: Witches and Bandits and Swords (Oh My) Chapter 1 Dev Play
snippet.description:
The first chapter of Witches and Bandits and Swords (Oh My) as narrated by Dominic O'Reilly of the world famous(ish) Krunchy Fried Games. Fun and frolics will be had by all.
Play WABASOM on itchio: https://krunchyfriedgames.itch.io/witches-and-bandits-and-swords-oh-my
Check out our other games: https://krunchyfriedgames.itch.io
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/KFriedGames
